name: Ext_R4_ImplementationGuide_de_pa_code
title: Cross-version Extension for R4.ImplementationGuide.definition.parameter.code for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version extension represents ImplementationGuide.definition.parameter.code from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ImplementationGuide|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R5.

element.short: apply | path-resource | path-pages | path-tx-cache | expansion-parameter | rule-broken-links | generate-xml | generate-json | generate-turtle | html-template
element.definition: `ImplementationGuide.definition.parameter.code` maps to R5 `ImplementationGuide.definition.parameter.code`. Has no type mapping `code` removed the required value set binding to `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/guide-parameter-code|4.3.0`. So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget.
